      • applyService

        public <T> T applyService(java.util.function.Function<org.semanticweb.owlapi.reasoner.OWLReasoner,T> service)
        Creates a new buffering OWLReasoner using the internal OWLReasonerFactory, with the constrained ontology as the root ontology, then executes the specified reasoning service. The return value of service is relayed to the caller. After service returns, the reasoner is immediately disposed of.

      • builder

        public static OntologicalCPNet.Builder builder(CPNet baseCPNet,
                                               org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntology baseOntology)
        Returns a builder that builds an OntologicalCPNet upon the specified CPNet and base ontology. Any changes to baseOntology applied before invoking OntologicalCPNet.Builder.build() will take effect.

        The specified base ontology must be consistent and named (that is, baseOntology.getOntologyID().isAnonymous() must return false); if either condition is not satisfied, OntologicalCPNet.Builder.build() will throw an IllegalStateException.

        Parameters:
        baseCPNet - the parent object of the OntologicalCPNet instance to build
        baseOntology -
        Returns:
